  "}"}]], "Output",
 CellLabel->"Out[87]=",ExpressionUUID->"63049b25-3d06-42ec-a414-8d5200c98d22"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell["\<\
Plot is able to localize the variables in its first argument using the \
HoldAll attribute:\
