upon $MaxPrecision will not check this newly named symbol when performing \
computations.", "Text", FontColor -> RGBColor[
                    Rational[2, 3], 0, 0]]}, {
                    TextCell["Module", "Text"]}], BaselinePosition -> {1, 1}, 
                  Spacings -> 0]], 2 -> Dynamic[
